title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 30 2021
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 30 2021
description:
Clay and Buck consider another EIB Southern Command in the midst of Omicron. Comedian Adam Carolla on the hilarity (and hypocrisy) of the times. Enes Kanter "Freedom" becomes an American citizen. Former Speaker of the House Newt Gingrich weighs in on the issues of the day.
